    The data is generated using the Faker gem to simulate real-world data.
  </p>

  <h2>Data Sources</h2>
  <p>We use the Faker gem to generate the following datasets:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Car Manufacturers:</strong> Includes the name and country of each manufacturer.</li>
    <li><strong>Cars:</strong> Includes the name, year, and associated manufacturer for each car model.</li>
  </ul>

